{
  "texts": [
    "These can be integrated into the VR headset, e.g., HTC Vive Pro Eye, or used isolated.",
    "Despite the number of solutions combining both technologies having significantly increased, only a few of them fuse both features.",
    "However, the vast majority of research concerning eye-tracking nowadays is based on VR-integrated solutions.",
    "It represents 57.6% of the reviewed articles published in 2021 (Fig. 4), whereas research from 2019 was mainly dominated by custom and isolated eyetracking devices such as SensoMotoric Instruments (SMI).",
    "On the other hand, integrated solutions barely achieved the 6% of reviewed manuscripts in 2019, whereas it stood for the 28.8% of revised research from 2020."
  ]
}